Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Customer

  • public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
    This represents a Customer with existing transactions in the Moblima system. Each instance of Customer is defined by a unique combination of name, mobile number and email. Each instance holds a list of transactions, which represent the customer's booking history.
    Author:
    SS3 Group 6
